<%= provide(:title, "ホーム") %>

<div class="container text-center mt-5">
<%= image_tag 'home.png', class: 'img-fluid rounded', alt: 'Description of image' %>
  <!--<%= render "layouts/carousel" %>-->

  <h5 class="my-4">FE_EDってどんなサービス？</h5>
  <p class="mb-4">
    FE_EDでは、基本情報技術者試験を目指すエンジニアのために<br>
    過去の受講生が経験し、得た知識を残すフィードバックサイトです。
  </p>

  <div class="d-lg-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-5">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-3 mb-lg-0 me-3">
      <%= image_tag "book_gijutsusyo_web.png", alt: "", width: "200", height: "200", class: "rounded-circle mx-auto" %>
      <p class="mt-2">優秀な教材<br>学習サイトを共有</p>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-3 mb-lg-0 me-3">
      <%= image_tag "computer_tokui_boy.png", alt: "", width: "200", height: "200", class: "rounded-circle mx-auto" %>
      <p class="mt-2">これまで受講してきた<br>仲間の経験談を学習に活かせる</p>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-3 mb-lg-0 me-3">
      <%= image_tag "juken_goukakuhappyou_happy.png", alt: "", width: "200", height: "200", class: "rounded-circle mx-auto" %>
      <p class="mt-2">最短合格<br>資格取得でエンジニアを目指そう！</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h5 class="my-4">FE_EDを始める</h5>

  <div class="mb-4">
    <%= link_to "新規登録", signup_path, class: "btn btn-success me-2" %>
    <%= link_to "ログイン", login_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
  </div>

</div>
